11#include "rtc_base/rtc_certificate.h"
12
13#include <memory>
14
15#include "rtc_base/checks.h"
16#include "rtc_base/ssl_certificate.h"
17#include "rtc_base/ssl_identity.h"
18#include "rtc_base/time_utils.h"
19
20namespace rtc {
21
22scoped_refptr<RTCCertificate> RTCCertificate::Create(
23 std::unique_ptr<SSLIdentity> identity) {
24 return new RTCCertificate(identity.release());
25}
26
27RTCCertificate::RTCCertificate(SSLIdentity* identity) : identity_(identity) {
28 RTC_DCHECK(identity_);
29}
30
31RTCCertificate::~RTCCertificate() = default;
32
33uint64_t RTCCertificate::Expires() const {
34 int64_t expires = GetSSLCertificate().CertificateExpirationTime();
35 if (expires != -1)
36 return static_cast<uint64_t>(expires) * kNumMillisecsPerSec;
37 // If the expiration time could not be retrieved return an expired timestamp.
38 return 0; // = 1970-01-01
39}
40
41bool RTCCertificate::HasExpired(uint64_t now) const {
42 return Expires() <= now;
43}
44
45const SSLCertificate& RTCCertificate::GetSSLCertificate() const {
46 return identity_->certificate();
47}
48
49// Deprecated: TODO(benwright) - Remove once chromium is updated.
50const SSLCertificate& RTCCertificate::ssl_certificate() const {
51 return identity_->certificate();
52}
53
54const SSLCertChain& RTCCertificate::GetSSLCertificateChain() const {
55 return identity_->cert_chain();
56}
57
58RTCCertificatePEM RTCCertificate::ToPEM() const {
59 return RTCCertificatePEM(identity_->PrivateKeyToPEMString(),
60 GetSSLCertificate().ToPEMString());
61}
62
63scoped_refptr<RTCCertificate> RTCCertificate::FromPEM(
64 const RTCCertificatePEM& pem) {
65 std::unique_ptr<SSLIdentity> identity(
66 SSLIdentity::CreateFromPEMStrings(pem.private_key(), pem.certificate()));
67 if (!identity)
68 return nullptr;
69 return new RTCCertificate(identity.release());
70}
71
72bool RTCCertificate::operator==(const RTCCertificate& certificate) const {
73 return *this->identity_ == *certificate.identity_;
74}
75
76bool RTCCertificate::operator!=(const RTCCertificate& certificate) const {
77 return !(*this == certificate);
78}
79
80} // namespace rtc
